                    משכבו<lb/> בשלום<lb/> של יודן<lb/> בן לוי </p>
         </div>
         <div type="translation" ana="#b1" xml:id="beth0227.translation" corresp="#beth0227.transcription">
            <p>This is the <rs type="object" ana="interpretations.xml#grave">resting place </rs> of <name type="patr">
                  <persName xml:lang="hbo " ref="persons.xml#beth0227p01">Yudan </persName>
                  <rs type="family" ana="interpretations.xml#son">son </rs> of <persName type="patr" xml:lang="hbo " ref="persons.xml#beth0227p02">Levi </persName>
               </name>
                    forever in <rs type="formula" ana="interpretations.xml#shalom">peace</rs>. May his resting place
                    be set (?) in peace. Of Yudan son of Levi.</p>
         </div>
